The paper involves the design and implementation of a deep learning-based RF signal classifier on an FPGA for real-time and low-power signal classification. This work involves aspects of machine learning (cs.LG), signal processing (cs.AR), embedded systems (cs.EM), network infrastructure (cs.NI), and control systems (cs.SY). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.LG and cs.AR, followed by cs.EM, cs.NI, and cs.SY.
